{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01GX9A9r1LreAtLr9zerTSgr","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All five files have been successfully created. Let me provide a summary of what was created:\n\n## Summary\n\nAll five Jakarta EE migration files have been successfully created in the specified directory:\n\n### Files Created:\n\n1. **DatabasePopulator.java** (5.0KB)\n   - Location: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/startup/DatabasePopulator.java`\n   - A Singleton EJB with @Startup that populates the database on application startup using Jakarta EE annotations\n\n2. **MarketSummarySingleton.java** (4.5KB)\n   - Location: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/MarketSummarySingleton.java`\n   - A Singleton EJB with scheduled tasks using Jakarta EE's @Schedule annotation\n\n3. **TradeSLSBBean.java** (21KB)\n   - Location: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/TradeSLSBBean.java`\n   - The main stateless session bean implementing TradeServices using Jakarta EE's @Transactional\n\n4. **AsyncScheduledOrderSubmitter.java** (1.5KB)\n   - Location: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrderSubmitter.java`\n   - Request-scoped bean for async order submission using Jakarta EE's ManagedExecutorService\n\n5. **AsyncScheduledOrder.java** (1.7KB)\n   - Location: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrder.java`\n   - Dependent-scoped Runnable for processing async orders\n\nAll files have been created with the exact content specified, using standard Jakarta EE annotations and APIs instead of Quarkus-specific implementations."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0505b85d-7bd5-4c52-85f6-40bd7ce1ee5d","uuid":"270d20be-e300-417d-9c44-32e62808df95"}
