{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01JEbw6dAcur8mwwwWpaCaaX","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've successfully created the file at `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/session2direct/DirectSLSBBean.java`.\n\nThe file contains the DirectSLSBBean class, which is part of the Jakarta EE migration of the Quarkus DayTrader application. This class:\n\n- Implements the TradeServices interface\n- Uses Jakarta EE annotations (@ApplicationScoped, @Inject)\n- Delegates all operations to the TradeDirect JDBC implementation via CDI injection\n- Is annotated with @TradeSession2Direct and @RuntimeMode(\"Session to Direct\") for runtime mode identification\n- Provides a complete delegation layer for all TradeServices methods including market operations, order management, account management, and quote operations"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0505b85d-7bd5-4c52-85f6-40bd7ce1ee5d","uuid":"ee3bbb34-bfe2-46ca-9095-53b391bbd455"}
