{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_017PxbnpMHPTMZrPUbwAbYSm","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully created the file `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/jaxrs/TradeResource.java` with the exact content you specified.\n\n## Summary\n\nThe file has been created as a JAX-RS resource class for DayTrader trading operations. This is a Jakarta EE migration from Quarkus REST and includes:\n\n**Key Features:**\n- JAX-RS endpoints for trading operations (buy, sell, login, logout)\n- Account management endpoints (profile, holdings, orders)\n- Market summary and registration functionality\n- Uses Jakarta EE annotations (@Path, @GET, @POST, @Inject, etc.)\n- CDI injection for TradeServices instances\n- JSON response format with error handling\n\n**File Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/jaxrs/TradeResource.java`\n\n**File Size:** 8.0K\n\nThe file has been successfully written with all the imports, annotations, and methods as specified in your request."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0505b85d-7bd5-4c52-85f6-40bd7ce1ee5d","uuid":"e448d8f1-e9e9-4381-8f45-b10b68fc4c7c"}
