{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Ab1vCKGdsTVK43rvJHYevv","type":"tool_result","content":"358:    public AccountDataBean getAccountData(String userID) {\n359-        AccountProfileDataBean profile = entityManager.find(AccountProfileDataBean.class, userID);\n360-        AccountDataBean account = profile.getAccount();\n361-        account.setProfileID(profile.getUserID());\n362-        return account;\n363-    }\n364-\n365-    @Override\n366-    public AccountProfileDataBean getAccountProfileData(String userID) {\n367-        return entityManager.find(AccountProfileDataBean.class, userID);\n368-    }\n369-\n370-    @Override\n371-    public AccountProfileDataBean updateAccountProfile(AccountProfileDataBean profileData) {\n372-        AccountProfileDataBean temp = entityManager.find(AccountProfileDataBean.class, profileData.getUserID());\n373-        temp.setAddress(profileData.getAddress());"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0505b85d-7bd5-4c52-85f6-40bd7ce1ee5d","uuid":"d91b0d2b-a4c7-43ed-80be-f9e6fe0bea9a"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_011vve7p12wqX7Kn3qeg2j5e","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issue is clear: `profile.getAccount()` returns null. This is because the `@OneToOne(mappedBy = \"profile\")` on `AccountProfileDataBean` is the inverse side of the relationship. The owning side is `AccountDataBean.profile` with `@JoinColumn(name = \"PROFILE_USERID\")`. \n\nEclipseLink should be able to resolve the inverse side through a query, but with `LAZY` fetch and possibly some EclipseLink-specific behavior, it might not load it. The fix is to either:\n1. Change the fetch type to `EAGER` on the inverse side\n2. Or use a query to find the account by profile userID\n\nLet me fix the `AccountProfileDataBean` to use `EAGER` fetch for the account relationship:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":720,"cache_read_input_tokens":97671,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":720,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":344},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0505b85d-7bd5-4c52-85f6-40bd7ce1ee5d","uuid":"70d77ba5-5826-4552-8140-b2510ac485bb"}
