{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_015xTEKWeYinHtMcGcYHug8E","type":"tool_result","content":"    95→    @Override\n    96→    public MarketSummaryDataBean getMarketSummary() {\n    97→        return marketSummarySingleton.getMarketSummaryDataBean();\n    98→    }\n    99→\n   100→    @Override\n   101→    @NotNull\n   102→    public OrderDataBean buy(String userID, String symbol, double quantity, int orderProcessingMode) {\n   103→        OrderDataBean order = null;\n   104→        BigDecimal total;\n   105→        try {\n   106→            AccountProfileDataBean profile = entityManager.find(AccountProfileDataBean.class, userID);\n   107→            AccountDataBean account = profile.getAccount();\n   108→            QuoteDataBean quote = entityManager.find(QuoteDataBean.class, symbol);\n   109→            HoldingDataBean holding = null;\n   110→\n   111→            order = createOrder(account, quote, holding, \"buy\", quantity);\n   112→\n   113→            BigDecimal price = quote.getPrice();\n   114→            BigDecimal orderFee = order.getOrderFee();\n   115→            BigDecimal balance = account.getBalance();\n   116→            total = (new BigDecimal(quantity).multiply(price)).add(orderFee);\n   117→            account.setBalance(balance.subtract(total));\n   118→            final Integer orderID = order.getOrderID();\n   119→\n   120→            if (orderProcessingMode == TradeConfig.SYNCH) {\n   121→                completeOrder(orderID, false);\n   122→            } else if (orderProcessingMode == TradeConfig.ASYNCH) {\n   123→                completeOrderAsync(orderID, false);\n   124→            } else if (orderProcessingMode == TradeConfig.ASYNCH_2PHASE) {\n   125→                queueOrder(orderID, true);\n   126→            }\n   127→        } catch (Exception e) {\n   128→            Log.error(\"TradeSLSBBean:buy(\" + userID + \",\" + symbol + \",\" + quantity + \") --> failed\", e);\n   129→            throw new RuntimeException(e);\n   130→        }\n   131→        return order;\n   132→    }\n   133→\n   134→    @Override\n   135→    @NotNull\n   136→    public OrderDataBean sell(final String userID, final Integer holdingID, int orderProcessingMode) {\n   137→        OrderDataBean order = null;\n   138→        BigDecimal total;\n   139→        try {\n   140→            AccountProfileDataBean profile = entityManager.find(AccountProfileDataBean.class, userID);\n   141→            AccountDataBean account = profile.getAccount();\n   142→\n   143→            HoldingDataBean holding = entityManager.find(HoldingDataBean.class, holdingID);\n   144→\n   145→            if (holding == null) {\n   146→                Log.debug(\"TradeSLSBBean:sell User \" + userID + \" attempted to sell holding \" + holdingID + \" which has already been sold\");\n   147→                OrderDataBean orderData = new OrderDataBean();\n   148→                orderData.setOrderStatus(\"cancelled\");\n   149→                entityManager.persist(orderData);\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0505b85d-7bd5-4c52-85f6-40bd7ce1ee5d","uuid":"2378693f-ca53-405c-add4-7a8415ec6cc6"}
